(47,'第一届大学生交通科技大赛','2021-01-01 14:00:00','花园校区讲堂4',12,98,'<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:25.0pt;\nmso-line-height-rule:exactly;layout-grid-mode:char;mso-layout-grid-align:\nnone\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E;mso-font-kerning:1.0pt\">各学院团委：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">为培养大学生的科技创新精神和实践能力，提高大学生科学素养，促进大学生学术活动开展，同时为参加省级和国家级交通科技大赛进行人才选拔和培育，学校决定组织开展第一届大学生交通科技大赛。现将有关事项通知如下：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体;color:#3E3E3E\">一、组织单位<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">主办单位：校团委<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>&nbsp; </span></span>土木与交通学院<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">大赛组委会：由校团委、土木与交通学院相关工作人员组成<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体;color:#3E3E3E\">二、竞赛日程与安排<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体;color:#3E3E3E\">报名及审核：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">即日</span><span style=\"font-size:\n14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312\">起至<span lang=\"EN-US\">2019</span><span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>日止，逾期视为自动放弃。各参赛队需将报名表（附件）电子档发送至<span lang=\"EN-US\">247007491@qq.com</span>邮箱，报名表电子档以“交通科技大赛报名表<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>学院名称<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>申报者姓名”命名。纸质报名表递交至花园校区<span lang=\"EN-US\">2313</span>室，联系人：董老师。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\n黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体\">作品初审：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312\">各参赛队于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2019</span><span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span>日上午<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>点前</span>将参赛作品提交至<span>花园校区<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>号教学楼<span lang=\"EN-US\">2407</span>室</span>，联系人郭老师。组委会将组织相关专业专家老师对参赛作品进行初评，提出评审意见，并确定、公布进入校终审作品名单。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体\">作品终审：</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">2019</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">14:00</span>举</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312\">行作品终审。进入终审环节的各参赛队携带参赛作品提前半小时到达现场，届时，专家组将对作品进行终审评测，终审环节具体地点另行通知。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:黑体;mso-bidi-font-family:黑体\">三、参赛说明<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">1.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">参赛对象<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">我校各学院正式注册的在校专、本科生均可参赛，</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312\">每支参赛小组指导教师不超过<span lang=\"EN-US\">2 </span>人，每小组成员限<span lang=\"EN-US\">2-5 </span>人，且每位同学只允许参加一支队伍。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">2.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">作品范围<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">参赛作品必须是<span lang=\"EN-US\">2018</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>月之后立项、<span lang=\"EN-US\">2019</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月之前完成的成果。参赛作品形式包括设计图纸、研究报告、实物模型、计算机软件等。所有作品应为原创，填写申报书并且撰写研究报告或论文。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">、作品分组<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">根据作品研究领域原则上分设<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>个竞赛小组，分别为：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\n宋体;color:#3E3E3E\">※</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\"> 交通运输规划与管理；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\n宋体;color:#3E3E3E\">※ </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">交通信息工程及控制；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\n宋体;color:#3E3E3E\">※ </span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">载运工具运用工程；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">※ 道路与铁道工程及其他。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">决赛时具体分组可视作品的具体数量以及类型进行调整。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:28.1pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:125%\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:125%;font-family:黑体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:黑体;color:#3E3E3E\">四、奖项设置<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.5pt;line-height:25.0pt;mso-line-height-rule:\nexactly\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;color:#3E3E3E\">本次比</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\nmso-bidi-font-family:仿宋_GB2312\">赛设一等奖、二等奖、三等奖若干。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"