(48,'第一届程序设计大赛','2020-05-30 14:00:00','花园校区东机房',1,100,'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">一、参赛流程<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">、参赛报名：各参赛选手请于在<span lang=\"EN-US\">2018</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">05</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">02</span>日前，登录<span lang=\"EN-US\">www.ncwu.club/hell </span>填写报名信息。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">、正式比赛：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2018</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">05</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">03</span>日下午<span lang=\"EN-US\">13:00-17:00</span>于华北水利水电大学（花园校区）东机房二楼举办。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">、组委会将于比赛结束后，对各参赛选手提交的程序代码进行查重，查重结束后，根据每位参赛者的比赛排名，确定获奖名单。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">二、比赛规则<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n宋体\">比赛以个人为单位，设置<span lang=\"EN-US\">8-10</span>个命题（含英文题），比赛时间为<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>个小时，比赛提供的编译环境为<span lang=\"EN-US\">Visual C++ 6.0</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">Devc++</span>、<span lang=\"EN-US\">myeclipse</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">．参赛者不能携带任何可用于计算机处理的软件或数据工具（不允许携带<span lang=\"EN-US\">U</span>盘或计数器）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">．比赛时只可登陆竞赛网站，不能浏览无关比赛的网页。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">．比赛时可以携带纸质书籍或资料（如书、程序清单、英语词典、草稿纸等），但不能携带任何电子程序资料。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">．参赛者不能携带任何类型的通讯工具（手机一律关机），比赛时禁用<span lang=\"EN-US\">QQ</span>等聊天工具，禁止收发任何方式的邮件和短信<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>违规者将被取消参赛资格。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">6.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n宋体\">在竞赛中，参赛者不得与其他参赛者以及组委会指定工作人员以外的人员交谈；工作人员仅可以回答和系统相关的问题，例如解释系统错误信息。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">7.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n宋体\">竞赛预定时间为<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>小时。比赛过程中若出现不可预见事件，组委会有权视情况需要调整竞赛时间。一旦竞赛时间发生改变，将会及时告知所有参赛者。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">8.</span><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:\n宋体\">比赛评判系统采用国内领先技术，具有自动判别相似代码功能，有效杜绝抄袭作弊等行为，保证了比赛的公平公正性。同时组委会专设比赛违纪现象举报邮箱：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2412864341@qq.com</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">9</span><span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">．正式比赛时，迟到<span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span>分钟者不得参加竞赛。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">三、排名规则 <span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">竞赛评分根据每位参赛者解答竞赛题目的数量及解题程序算式所需时间长短进行排名。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）首先根据各参赛者解题数量进行排名；<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）若以上二者均相同，则根据参赛者解题用时加惩罚时进行排名。解题用时和惩罚时由每道解答正确试题用时加惩罚时两部分构成。每道试题用时从竞赛开始到试题解答被判为正确为止进行计时，期间每一次错误运行将被加罚<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>分钟，未正确解答试题不计时。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">四、评奖标准<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">大赛按参赛选手排名评奖，奖项设置为一等奖、二等奖、三等奖和优秀奖。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">五、注意事项<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:\n16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">、对于评判结果说明如下：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:宋体\">通过（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Accepted</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">AC</span>）、答案错误<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Wrong Answer</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">WA)</span>、超时<span lang=\"EN-US\">(Time Limit Exceed</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">TLE)</span>、超过输出限制（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Output Limit Exceed</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">OLE)</span>、超内存（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Memory Limit Exceed</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">MLE</span>）、运行时错误（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Runtime Error</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">RE</span>）、格式错误（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Presentation Error</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">PE)</span>、或是无法编译（<span lang=\"EN-US\">Compile Error</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">CE</span>），并返回程序使用的内存、运行时间等信息。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:32.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\nline-height:150%\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 32pt; font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">2</span><span style=\"text-indent: 32pt; font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;\">、菜单栏中<span lang=\"EN-US\">Standing</span>菜单可以实时查看实时排名</span></p><style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @font-face\n	{font-family:宋体;\n	panose-1:2 1 6